name: wolves can be sad too
description:
PSEUDO ANTROKIZM #36

A little rant
today, this second I'm angry with what I've ever done,, really I don't want to hurt other people, especially the woman I love, but for some reason I left her, one good reason, because I can 'Don't make her happy with what I have, while he always fulfills all his wishes from his parents,,, you know,, how I feel,, I'm afraid I can't fulfill his wishes,, that's why I left him,, but honestly, seeing him married I immediately returned everything memories of seven years ago,, long time together,, honestly I'm sick,, it hurts so much,, but this is for his happiness and my good

thank you for accompanying me, from scratch I couldn't design all this time,, you are the best by my side, and now there is someone better by your side

good luck and stay happy

and I'm very sorry, I'm sorry, please forgive and forgive everything that has been done to me.. quickly have a child ndul
